"## 1. Products of Sequences (The Big Boss!)\n"
"\n"
"We finish the **Algebraic Limit Theorem** by proving that products of convergent sequences converge:\n"
"- If `a n ‚Üí L` and `b n ‚Üí M`, then `a n * b n ‚Üí L * M`\n"
