"   - `intro Œµ hŒµ` handled 'for every Œµ > 0'\n"
"   - `use 1` provided the witness `N` (any number works!)\n"
"   - `intro n hn` handled '‚àÄ n ‚â• N'\n"
"   - Then algebraic manipulation showed that `|a n - L| = |L - L| = |0|`\n"
